# Decisions - {{TASK_NAME}}

> **Decision records.** Numbered D1, D2, D3... When a decision is revised, the old block is
> NOT deleted - a new block `D<N>.<M>` is added on top of it, referencing the original.
> The history of *why it was "this way" and became "that way"* matters as much as the current state.

## Revision format

```markdown
## D1.1. [Revises D1, <date>] <New decision>

**Re-evaluation of D1** (<one-line summary of the original decision>).

**New decision:** <what was decided now>.

**Why revised:** <what changed; stakeholder quote if there was one>.

**What happens to artifacts built under D1:** <rebuild / obsolete / still valid>.
```

